data.description: So inviting is this 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath home. Covered front porch to welcoming front foyer w/nook area and eye-catching stair case. Double French doors w/glass lead to an extra-large, window/light filled living room, and adjacent dining room. Kitchen is good space w/breakfast bar area and large pantry/storage. There are three bedrooms up with great closet space (3 walk-ins), some built-in's and rear porch. Full bath is up and updated plus half bath on main level. Yard is partially fenced with a roomy 2.75 car garage, and additional parking space. This home has some newer windows throughout, all freshly painted, central air, etc.
